Class rankingStore

java.lang.Object
com.comp2059.app.rankingStore
public class rankingStore extends Object
This class contain some methods used to store the ranking information. Store structure: player-name, destroyed-asteroid-number, beaten-boss-number, live-time, total-score

      public static void addresult​(String player_name, int destroyed_asteroid_number, int beaten_boss_number, String live_time, int total_score)
      This function is used to insert the new record into the ranking.
      Parameters:
      player_name - user's name.
      destroyed_asteroid_number - destroyed asteroid number from the game.
      beaten_boss_number - beaten boss number from the game.
      live_time - total time user survive in the game.
      total_score - total score of game from asteroid and boss.
